From: "=a

Subject: Request re Maxwell Laptop 
Date: Tue, 10 Aug 2021 20:27:34 +0000 
Hope you're doing well. Ghislaine Maxwell's attorney has informed me that Maxwell is having difficulty reviewing the 
portions of her discovery that include audio recordings on the laptop my office provided for her use. The attorney seems 
to think that the issue can be fixed if someone from MDC's IT department could assist Maxwell in enabling the audio jack 
so that Maxwell can use headphones to listen to the recordings. Would it be possible to ask someone from IT to please 
look into this issue? 
Thanks very much, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
New York, NY 10007 
M6 
EFTA00027305
